          <h1>Who’s to Say Sports Path</h1>
          <p class="program-subtitle">
            Sports create belonging. This pathway supports inclusive participation — from community play to
            meaningful roles alongside high school teams — so connection doesn’t end at graduation.
          </p>

          <div class="btn-row">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#get-started">Get Started</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#for-schools">For Schools</a>
          </div>

          <div class="best-for-inline">
            <strong>Best for:</strong> participants who love teams, routines, game-day energy, community pride, and sports storytelling.
          </div>

          <div class="pills" aria-label="Highlights">
